title: 2 Million Bikers to DC
subtitle: Was the '2 Millions Bikers to DC' group denied a 'no-stop' permit for a Washington ride-through on 11 September 2013?
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: The "2 Millions Bikers to DC" group has been denied a "no-stop" permit for a Washington ride-through on 11 September 2013.
